Wednesday, March 27, 1996

MERIT DOCKET

95-1536. ALLTEL Ohio, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 94-2012-TP-ACE. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

*1421Moyer, C.J., Douglas, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur. Resnick, J., not participating.
